title: Ben Carson leads Republicans in fundraising as Ted Cruz quietly fills war chest
text: In a summer for political outsiders, retired surgeon Ben Carson far out-raised his Republican rivals in a crowded field, hauling in $20 million. But it's his fellow political insurgent Sen. Ted Cruz (R-Texas) who ended the quarter with the most cash in the bank. Cruz, the first-term Texas senator... ...
